64#ifndef ARRAY_SIZE

68#ifndef BIT
69#define BIT(a) (1 << (a))
70#endif
71
72#define BIT_SET(reg, bit) (reg |= (bit))
73#define BIT_CLR(reg, bit) (reg &= ~(bit))
74#define WAIT_BIT_SET(reg, bit) while (!(reg & bit))
75#define WAIT_BIT_CLR(reg, bit) while (reg & bit)

199#define __STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_MAIN (0x01)
200#define __STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_SUB1 (0x05)
201#define __STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_SUB2 (0x00)
202#define __STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_RC (0x00)
203#define __STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION ((__STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_MAIN << 24)\
204 |(__STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_SUB1 << 16)\
205 |(__STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_SUB2 << 8)\
206 |(__STM32F0XX_STDPERIPH_VERSION_RC))

2692/******************************************************************************/
2693/* */
2694/* CRS Clock Recovery System */
2695/* (Available only for STM32F072 devices) */
2696/******************************************************************************/
2697
2698/******************* Bit definition for CRS_CR register *********************/
2699#define CRS_CR_SYNCOKIE ((uint32_t)0x00000001) /* SYNC event OK interrupt enable */
2700#define CRS_CR_SYNCWARNIE ((uint32_t)0x00000002) /* SYNC warning interrupt enable */
2701#define CRS_CR_ERRIE ((uint32_t)0x00000004) /* SYNC error interrupt enable */
2702#define CRS_CR_ESYNCIE ((uint32_t)0x00000008) /* Expected SYNC(ESYNCF) interrupt Enable*/
2703#define CRS_CR_CEN ((uint32_t)0x00000020) /* Frequency error counter enable */
2704#define CRS_CR_AUTOTRIMEN ((uint32_t)0x00000040) /* Automatic trimming enable */
2705#define CRS_CR_SWSYNC ((uint32_t)0x00000080) /* A Software SYNC event is generated */
2706#define CRS_CR_TRIM ((uint32_t)0x00003F00) /* HSI48 oscillator smooth trimming */
2707
2708/******************* Bit definition for CRS_CFGR register *********************/
2709#define CRS_CFGR_RELOAD ((uint32_t)0x0000FFFF) /* Counter reload value */
2710#define CRS_CFGR_FELIM ((uint32_t)0x00FF0000) /* Frequency error limit */
2711#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCDIV ((uint32_t)0x07000000) /* SYNC divider */
2712#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCDIV_0 ((uint32_t)0x01000000) /* Bit 0 */
2713#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCDIV_1 ((uint32_t)0x02000000) /* Bit 1 */
2714#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCDIV_2 ((uint32_t)0x04000000) /* Bit 2 */
2715#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCSRC ((uint32_t)0x30000000) /* SYNC signal source selection */
2716#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCSRC_0 ((uint32_t)0x10000000) /* Bit 0 */
2717#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCSRC_1 ((uint32_t)0x20000000) /* Bit 1 */
2718#define CRS_CFGR_SYNCPOL ((uint32_t)0x80000000) /* SYNC polarity selection */
2719
2720/******************* Bit definition for CRS_ISR register *********************/
2721#define CRS_ISR_SYNCOKF ((uint32_t)0x00000001) /* SYNC event OK flag */
2722#define CRS_ISR_SYNCWARNF ((uint32_t)0x00000002) /* SYNC warning */
2723#define CRS_ISR_ERRF ((uint32_t)0x00000004) /* SYNC error flag */
2724#define CRS_ISR_ESYNCF ((uint32_t)0x00000008) /* Expected SYNC flag */
2725#define CRS_ISR_SYNCERR ((uint32_t)0x00000100) /* SYNC error */
2726#define CRS_ISR_SYNCMISS ((uint32_t)0x00000200) /* SYNC missed */
2727#define CRS_ISR_TRIMOVF ((uint32_t)0x00000400) /* Trimming overflow or underflow */
2728#define CRS_ISR_FEDIR ((uint32_t)0x00008000) /* Frequency error direction */
2729#define CRS_ISR_FECAP ((uint32_t)0xFFFF0000) /* Frequency error capture */
2730
2731/******************* Bit definition for CRS_ICR register *********************/
2732#define CRS_ICR_SYNCOKC ((uint32_t)0x00000001) /* SYNC event OK clear flag */
2733#define CRS_ICR_SYNCWARNC ((uint32_t)0x00000002) /* SYNC warning clear flag */
2734#define CRS_ICR_ERRC ((uint32_t)0x00000004) /* Error clear flag */
2735#define CRS_ICR_ESYNCC ((uint32_t)0x00000008) /* Expected SYNC clear flag */
2736
